
Metron::Kafka
=================================

<Insert plugin documentation here.>

```
cd bro-kafka
./configure --bro-dist=/home/vagrant/bro-2.4.1 --with-librdkafka=/usr/lib64
make
```

Create a bro script as follows.  Ultimately, this will likely become
`/usr/local/bro/share/bro/site/local.bro`.

```
@load base/protocols/http
@load base/protocols/dns

@load-plugin Metron::Kafka
@load Metron/Kafka/logs-to-kafka.bro

redef Kafka::streams_to_include = set(HTTP::LOG, DNS::LOG);
redef Kafka::kafka_broker_list = "localhost:9092";
redef Kafka::topic_name = "bro";
```

```
export BRO_PLUGIN_PATH="/home/vagrant/bro-kafka/build/"
bro -NN Metron::Kafka
sudo -E /usr/local/bro/bin/bro -b local.bro -i eth0
```
